data.description: Welcome Home to this cozy 3 Bed 2 Bath single-story gem located in highly sought after Heritage Neighborhood and backing up to green belt; Private gate to the green belt & no rear neighbors! Located in the highly-rated Keller Independent School District, this home is just walking distance from top-rated School, and minutes to shopping & dining options. INCLUDED IN HOA DUES residents have access to incredible community pools and water slides, clubhouse, walking trails, a playground and tennis courts. There’s a workout room with equipment, sand volleyball, the clubhouse is always open with a coffee machine. You can go work in there or meet people. This is a MUST-SEE home in a great location!
